{"tid":780296,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"棲息地減　河馬酒店外覓食","createTime":"2018-08-15T05:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T05:44:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d36c512dac94de56ebdb542ea2172f490141b1b3","tid":780296,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180815/20476627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180815%2F20476627&d=Dfr5vMQy2Fz3sieZCL%2FyEgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=7feb6238\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180815%2F20476627&h=fba23590\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180815/20476627</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月15日 <br />\n<br />\n棲息地減　河馬酒店外覓食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180815/large/15ck1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180815%2Flarge%2F15ck1p.jpg&h=7c9e8791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■河馬棲息地減少，覓食難，與人類衝突日增。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n非洲每年約有500人因河馬襲擊致死，肯雅今年已有6宗死亡個案，台客遇襲或與河馬棲息地被侵犯有關。當地傳媒報道，奈瓦薩湖周邊的地產過度開發，河馬棲息地減少，加上近來肯雅暴雨令水面升高，湖岸四周植物流失，飢餓的河馬為覓食，被迫靠近農場與酒店，對人類帶來威脅。<br />\n<br />\n河馬是世界上最危險的動物之一，擁有鋒利的牙齒及強而有力的下顎，奈瓦薩湖船東協會成員奇洛（David Kilo）表示：「河馬是在酒店附近找牧草，這已經不是第一次了。這座湖畔，人類與野生動物的衝突越來越多，主因就是湖畔土地漸遭佔據。」　<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n肯雅政府擊斃殺台客河馬　民眾不滿觸發反華情緒<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n穗湖南工人染恙蟲病　延醫10日不治"},{"pid":"c1f3bb5c871882e14b3076f4dd9c15bb81d248e4","tid":780296,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea903d69c3a7a001c1de5f2e012e164dd59e917","tid":780296,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"真魔獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}